summary: Interventional Cardiologist at Albert Schweitzer Hospital, Dordrecht. I am also trained as clinical epidemiologist. My research focusses on intracoronary imaging with intravascular ultrasound and near-infrared spectroscopy, percutaneous coronary intervention, cardiovascular biomarkers and cardiogenic shock.
